#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"~]#&nbsp;<command>ip link set dev em1 down</command>\n"
"~]#&nbsp;<command>ip link set dev em1 master team0</command>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add additional ports as required. Team driver will bring ports up "
"automatically."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#, no-c-format
msgid "Listing the ports of a Team Using teamnl"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view or list the ports in a network team, using the <application>teamnl</"
"application> utility, issue the following command as <systemitem class="
