#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Where <replaceable>JSON-config-string</replaceable> is the configuration as "
"a string of text in JSON format. This will update the configuration of the "
"port using the JSON format string supplied. An example of a valid JSON "
"string for configuring a port would be the following:"
