#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The team daemon <systemitem class=\"daemon\">teamd</systemitem> sends an ARP "
"REQUEST to an address at the remote end of the link in order to determine if "
"the link is up. The method used is the same as the <application>arping</"
"application> utility but it does not use that utility."
